article.description: — Yvan Ouedraogo had 11 points and 10 rebounds to lift Grand Canyon to a 65-51 win over North Florida on Friday night.
article.headline: Ouedraogo lifts Grand Canyon past North Florida 65-51
article.linkText: Ouedraogo lifts Grand Canyon past North Florida 65-51
article.story: PHOENIX -- — Yvan Ouedraogo had 11 points and 10 rebounds to lift Grand Canyon to a 65-51 win over North Florida on Friday night. Jovan Blacksher Jr. had 12 points for Grand Canyon (2-0). Sean Miller-Moore added 10 points. Gabe McGlothan had nine rebounds. Carter Hendricksen had 18 points for the Ospreys (0-3). Dorian James added 10 points and seven rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25------ Information from: Automated Insights, http://automatedinsights.com/ ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
